class.name: Double5Function

javadoc.text: Interface that represents a function object: a function that takes * 5 arguments and returns a single value.
Applies a function to two arguments.
javadoc.param: a the first argument passed to the function.
b the second argument passed to the function.
c the third argument passed to the function.
d the fourth argument passed to the function.
e the fifth argument passed to the function.
